<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>The PM Hub: Project Management Community</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;0,800;1,700;1,800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:          #f0ebe0;
      --bg-light:    #ede8dd;
      --navy:        #0d1526;
      --navy-card:   #111f38;
      --navy-input:  #0f1a2e;
      --border-navy: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      --border-light: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      --orange:      #e8692a;
      --orange-dark: #b84f1a;
      --text-dark:   #1a1a2e;
      --text-mid:    #555566;
      --text-light:  #8892a4;
      --white:       #ffffff;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 1.25rem;
      height: 64px;
      background: var(--navy);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-logo-box {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      background: #162040;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .nav-logo-box .logo-pm {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1;
      text-align: center;
      display: block;
    }
    .nav-logo-box .logo-hub {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--orange);
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .nav-wordmark {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .nav-wordmark em {
      font-style: italic;
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      color: var(--orange);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .nav-apply {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-apply:hover { background: #d05a22; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 100px 1.75rem 80px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    /* warm peach glow at bottom */
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -40px; left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 90%;
      height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(232,105,42,0.2) 0%, rgba(232,105,42,0.05) 50%, transparent 75%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius: 100px;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .hero-badge-dot {
      width: 7px; height: 7px;
      background: var(--orange);
      border-radius: 50%;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .hero-badge span {
      font-size: 0.67rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 9vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.08;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--orange);
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .btn-orange {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-orange:hover { background: #d05a22; }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text-dark);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }

    /* ── LOGO CARD ── */
    .logo-card-wrap {
      padding: 0 1.5rem 2.5rem;
      background: var(--bg);
    }

    .logo-card {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--orange);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--navy);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 260px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .logo-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 50% 50%, rgba(232,105,42,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }

    .logo-card-inner {
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .logo-big {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .logo-big .the { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-light); vertical-align: super; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .logo-big .pm { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #fff; }
    .logo-big .hub { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic; color: var(--orange); }

    .logo-sub {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    /* ── FEATURE CARDS ── */
    .features-wrap {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 0 1.5rem 1rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      background: var(--navy-card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    .section {
      padding: 3rem 1.75rem;
      background: var(--navy);
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--orange);
      margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 7vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .section p.lead {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* ── FORM BOX ── */
    .form-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--navy-input);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.65rem 0.9rem;
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .form-group input::placeholder,
    .form-group textarea::placeholder { color: #4a5568; }

    .form-group input:focus,
    .form-group textarea:focus { border-color: rgba(232,105,42,0.5); }

    .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }

    .btn-submit-orange {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
    .btn-submit-orange:hover { background: #d05a22; }

    .btn-submit-dark {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--orange-dark);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      padding: 0.85rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }
    .btn-submit-dark:hover { background: #9a4016; }

    /* ── SLOTS ── */
    .slots-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .slots-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .slot {
      background: var(--navy-input);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 0.65rem 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .slot:hover, .slot.active {
      border-color: var(--orange);
      color: var(--orange);
      background: rgba(232,105,42,0.07);
    }

    /* ── OR LABEL ── */
    .or-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--orange);
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0.6rem;
    }

    /* ── BULLETS ── */
    .bullet-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .bullet-list li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .bullet-list li::before {
      content: '→';
      color: var(--orange);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: var(--navy);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-logo-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .footer-logo-box {
      width: 30px; height: 30px;
      background: #162040;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .footer-logo-box span { font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1; }
    .footer-logo-box em { font-style: normal; font-size: 0.5rem; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 600; }

    footer p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; }

    .icon { display: inline-block; width: 1.4rem; height: 1.4rem; stroke: var(--orange); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.8; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; vertical-align: middle; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-box">
        <span class="logo-pm">PM</span>
        <span class="logo-hub">Hub</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-wordmark">THE PM.<em>HUB</em></div>
    </a>
    <a href="#join" class="nav-apply">Apply &nbsp;→</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <div class="hero-badge-dot"></div>
      <span>Project Management Community</span>
    </div>
    <h1>A community for the <em>next generation</em> of project managers.</h1>
    <p>Whether you're in college, finishing university, or pivoting from another career. The PM Hub is a safe space to network, share ideas, ask the questions you've been holding back, and build the confidence to land your first PM role.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#join" class="btn-orange">Request to join &nbsp;→</a>
      <a href="#members" class="btn-outline">For Members</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOGO CARD -->
  <div class="logo-card-wrap">
    <div class="logo-card">
      <div class="logo-card-inner">
        <div class="logo-big">
          <span class="the">THE</span><span class="pm">PM.</span><span class="hub">Hub</span>
        </div>
        <div class="logo-sub">Project Management Community</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FEATURE CARDS -->
  <div class="features-wrap">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M3 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75M21 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.85"/></svg>
      <h3>Network with peers</h3>
      <p>Aspiring PMs across every industry: finance, tech, healthcare, construction and beyond.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
      <h3>Real guidance</h3>
      <p>Practical, honest advice from people who've walked the path you're starting.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-card">
      <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      <h3>A safe space</h3>
      <p>Ask anything. Share anything. No gatekeeping, no judgment. Just encouragement.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- JOIN SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="join">
    <div class="section-label">01: Apply</div>
    <h2>Request to join the community</h2>
    <p class="lead">Tell me a little about you and where you are in your PM journey. I read every application personally and reach out within a few days.</p>

    <form class="form-box" action="https://formspree.io/f/xlgvnegy" method="POST" id="join-form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="join-name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="join-name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="join-age">Age</label>
        <input type="text" id="join-age" name="age" placeholder="e.g. 24" required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="join-role">Current role</label>
        <input type="text" id="join-role" name="current_role" placeholder="Student, Analyst, Coordinator..." required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="join-industry">Industry</label>
        <input type="text" id="join-industry" name="industry" placeholder="Tech, Healthcare, Construction..." required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="join-help">What can The PM Hub help you with?</label>
        <textarea id="join-help" name="how_can_we_help" placeholder="Career pivot, interview prep, networking, certifications, day-in-the-life questions..." required></textarea>
      </div>
      <div id="join-success" style="display:none; color:#e8692a; font-size:0.9rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; font-weight:500;">
        Thanks! Your request has been received. I'll be in touch within a few days.
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-submit-orange">Request to join</button>
    </form>

    <div class="or-label">Or: Book a chat</div>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.9rem; margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Schedule a 1-1 with me</h2>
    <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:0;">Want to talk before applying? Pick a slot from my availability and I'll confirm by email.</p>

    <form class="form-box" id="chat-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xvzyrokr" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="Book a Chat" />
      <div class="slots-label">Pick a slot from my availability</div>
      <div class="slots-grid">
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 6:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 6:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 7:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 7:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 8:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 8:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Wed · 7:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Wed · 7:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Wed · 8:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Wed · 8:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 6:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 6:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 7:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 7:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 8:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Fri · 8:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 11:00 AM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 11:30 AM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 12:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 12:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 1:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 1:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 2:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 2:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 3:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 3:30 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 4:00 PM</button>
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Sat · 4:30 PM</button>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" name="selected_slot" id="chat-slot-value" />
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="chat-name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="chat-name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="chat-email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="chat-email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="chat-notes">Anything you'd like to cover? (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="chat-notes" name="notes" placeholder="e.g. interview prep for a PMO role"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div id="chat-success" style="display:none; color:#e8692a; font-size:0.9rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem; font-weight:500;">
        Booked! I'll confirm your slot by email within 24 hours.
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-submit-dark">Request meeting</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <!-- MEMBERS SECTION -->
  <section class="section" id="members" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
    <div class="section-label">02: For Members</div>
    <h2>Already in the Hub? Book your 1-1.</h2>
    <p class="lead">This section is what I share inside the community. Members can grab time with me whenever they need a sounding board: CV reviews, interview prep, career decisions, or just a pep talk.</p>

    <ul class="bullet-list">
      <li>30-minute focused sessions</li>
      <li>Confidential and judgment-free</li>
      <li>Bring an agenda or come open</li>
    </ul>

    <form class="form-box" id="member-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xvzyrokr" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="Member Booking" />
      <div class="slots-label">Pick a slot from my availability</div>
      <div class="slots-grid">
        <button class="slot" onclick="selectSlot(this)">Mon · 6:00 PM</button>
